TopicTitle: Space station explodes during time warp

Articles.Content:
EDIT: This appears to be The Kraken. Please move this thread to Support (unmodded). Thanks.

I have a space station that explodes when I time warp. It consists of:

2 hitch hiker compartments

1 battery

2 solar panels

1 monopropellent tank

4 RCS motors

5 docking ports

2 kerbals

Every time I warp, it explodes. It appears to be one of the hitch hiker compartments going first. The space station has been in orbit for the past human week, and has never exploded until today. Any suggestions what may cause this?

Station before explosion: http://cloud-4.steamusercontent.com/ugc/34109096034271468/6DA4B426A7A93526BCE871290AC3AA8A0878B228/

Station during explosion: http://cloud-4.steamusercontent.com/ugc/34109096034270678/9C24CD765D62DB65298E6F56E4E873113D177E69/

- - - Updated - - -

After many repeats, I was able to see that the station breaks into components, like two magnets repelling each other.

- - - Updated - - -

On a few rare occasion it just falls apart instead of exploding. See this photo: http://cloud-4.steamusercontent.com/ugc/34109096034322529/6741D7FB37ABCEB25760957BC30D2DCFC49985A3/

- - - Updated - - -

Also, this is the stock game with no mods.

- - - Updated - - -
